+  "success_gate": "A real provider-backed agent performed the bounded runtime action in the intended repository, required validators passed, a coherent commit exists ahead of the recorded floor, and the certification report records exact evidence.",
+  "failure_rule": "Authentication, quota, network, unsupported adapter, dirty target, detached target, missing authority, failed spawn, missing action, failed validation, or missing commit is a blocker and never a certification pass."
+}
